General.Description: Semper Paratus Acquisition Corporation does not have significant operations. It intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. The company intends to acquire companies operating in the transportation, supply chain, and logistics industries. Semper Paratus Acquisition Corporation was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
